verbose_text: The fixed-dose, one-pill combination of grazoprevir (GZR), NS3/4A inhibitor, and elbasvir (EBR), which blocks the NS5A complex, was intended for GT1 and GT4 infected patients with standard therapy duration of 12 weeks, which assured an SVR rate over 95% [XREF_BIBR].
